<p>英 /'sɪɡnəl/    美 /'sɪɡnəl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-sign">1.★ <strong>信号；暗号(sign)；信号灯：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>digital TV signals
数字电视信号</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This was a <strong>signal for</strong> him to continue.
这是一个让他继续的信号。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 5</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>In our class, when the bell rang and the teacher closed his book, it was a signal <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ everyone to stand up.  （2009 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>